70 the implementation and administration of the provisions of this Code section.
71 (h) This Code section shall stand repealed and reserved on December 31, 2031."
72 SECTION 3.
73 This Act shall become effective on January 1, 2026, and shall be applicable to taxable years
74 beginning on or after January 1, 2026.
75 SECTION 4.
76 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
